name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: mapreduce.shuffle.ssl.file.buffer.size
description: Buffer size for reading spills from file when using SSL.

name: dfs.storage.policy.satisfier.max.outstanding.paths
description:
Defines the maximum number of paths to satisfy that can be queued up in the
    Satisfier call queue in a period of time. Default value is 10000.

name: mapreduce.job.speculative.retry-after-no-speculate
description:
The waiting time(ms) to do next round of speculation
  if there is no task speculated in this round.

name: fs.s3a.paging.maximum
description:
How many keys to request from S3 when doing
     directory listings at a time.

name: tfile.fs.output.buffer.size
description: Buffer size used for FSDataOutputStream in bytes.
